      <title>自2007年以来，元素跌至最弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/yuan-drops-to-weakest-since-2007-as-us-china-trade-war-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的陆上人民币降至近二十年来最弱的水平，没有迹象表明世界上两个最大经济体之间的贸易紧张局势陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/yuan-drops-to-weakest-since-2007-as-us-china-trade-war-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 01:39:00 GMT</pubDate>
